        <p>For more information, see the <a href='https://github.com/siteadmin/inferno#inferno' target="_blank">Inferno README</a> and the <a href='https://github.com/siteadmin/inferno/wiki' target='_blank'>Inferno wiki</a>.</p>
      </div>
